body_html:
rename ./tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/nsync/builds/default.linux.c++11/nsync.a to libnsync.a and then modify makefile -L$(DOWNLOADSDIR)/nsync/builds/default.linux.c++11/ -lnsync

I got the similar linking error when building label_image example for Raspberry Pi, but fixed it by following @liyungithub 's tips, thanks
